          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold">Revenue-Driving Web Apps</h3>
            <div class="text-green-400 text-sm font-medium">ROI: 150-300%</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
          Customer portals, e-commerce platforms, and web applications that directly drive revenue growth.
        </p>
        
        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Increase online conversions by 45%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
