            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Reduce churn rates by 35%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
